underlying_goal: User wanted to catalogue, critically evaluate, and reorganize the project's sandbagging prompts.
primary_success: Critically analyzed over 130 sandbagging prompts, identifying nonsensical 'fantasy mechanisms' and miscategorized prompts. This analysis enabled a major cleanup and reorganization of the prompt library.
brief_summary: User asked for a catalogue of all sandbagging prompts. Claude first provided a comprehensive list, then a critical assessment identifying which prompts were nonsensical or miscategorized. Based on user feedback, Claude then archived/moved/fixed the prompts and created a final `CATALOGUE.yaml` file to index the cleaned-up prompt set.
